. **** KOLM-SMIRNOV TEST OF EXPORT DISTRIBUTION AND GRAPHS *****
. label var dif_ln_imp_5 "Chinese Export Growth"

.          
. ksmirnov dif_ln_imp_5 if xtilesample, by(unc_3) 

Two-sample Kolmogorov–Smirnov test for equality of distribution functions

Smaller group             D     p-value  Corrected
--------------------------------------------------
1                    0.0703       0.001
3                   -0.0091       0.886
Combined K-S         0.0703       0.001      0.001

Note: Ties exist in combined dataset;
      there are 3209 unique values out of 3211 observations.

. local kspval=round(`r(p)',.001) 

.  
. twoway (kdensity dif_ln_imp_5 if unc_3 == 3 & xtilesample, kernel(epan) range
> (-5 7.5) ) (kdensity dif_ln_imp_5 if unc_3 == 1 & xtilesample,kernel(epan) ra
